{"word":"G3980 - πειθαρχέω - peitharchéō - pi-tharkh-eh'-o - Hearken","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πειθαρχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>peitharchéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pi-tharkh-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Hearken"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கீழ்ப்படி, சொல்லைக்கேள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to obey"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3982 - πείθω - peíthō - pi'-tho/3982\">G3982</a> and <a href=\"#/G757 - ἄρχω - árchō - ar'-kho/757\">G757</a>; to <i>be persuaded</i> by a <i>ruler</i>, that is, (generally) to <i>submit</i> to authority; by analogy to <i>conform</i> to advice: - hearken, obey (magistrates)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3980 - πειθαρχέω - peitharchéō - pi-tharkh-eh'-o/3980\">G3980</a>, <a href=\"#/G3981 - πειθός - peithós - pi-thos'/3981\">G3981</a>, <a href=\"#/G3982 - πείθω - peíthō - pi'-tho/3982\">G3982</a>, <a href=\"#/G3988 - πεισμονή - peismonḗ - pice-mon-ay'/3988\">G3988</a>, <a href=\"#/G4006 - πεποίθησις - pepoíthēsis - pep-oy'-thay-sis/4006\">G4006</a>, <a href=\"#/G543 - ἀπείθεια - apeítheia - ap-i'-thi-ah/543\">G543</a>, <a href=\"#/G544 - ἀπειθέω - apeithéō - ap-i-theh'-o/544\">G544</a>, <a href=\"#/G545 - ἀπειθής - apeithḗs - ap-i-thace'/545\">G545</a>"}]}